com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document

Interface SpenPaintingDoc.HistoryListener

  • Enclosing class:
    SpenPaintingDoc

    public static interface SpenPaintingDoc.HistoryListener
    This listener interface provides callback methods for receiving history events.
    The interface receives notifications when a new history event is committed by SpenPaintingDoc.commitHistory(HistoryUpdateInfo)
    Since:
    5.0.0
    See Also:
    SpenPaintingDoc.setHistoryListener(HistoryListener)
